WHAT IS STRING AND TYPES OF STRING ?

Anything represent in “  ”  (double quotes) is called as String. 
• With respect to java string is a inbuild class which is present in java 
library. 
• The string class contains inbuild methods using which we can perform 
operations on string value. 
• The string class methods can be used only on string value. 
• Some of the inbuild methods of string class are, 
1. int length () 
2. char charAt(int index) 
3. String toLowercase () 
4. String toUppercase () 
5. boolean equals (String s) 
6. String concat(String s) 
7. boolean startsWith (String s) 
8. boolean endsWith (String s) 
9. boolean equalsIgnorecase (String s) 
